Subject: Cannot Connect to SPO
Description: Hi team, we have tried to connect Netwrix to our SPO but we keep getting ACCESS DENIED errors. Could you please help me connect it?
What_We_Know__c: The issue is happening when customer does not have on prem AD and the SP bulk import jobs are running it looks for the tables that are getting created when ADI job runs.
Solution_Comment__c: R&D team provided scripts to create tables and SPs manually which fixed the issue.
